  "description": "<p>分类: <a href=\"http://cn.engadget.com/category/smartphones/\" rel=\"tag\">智能手机</a>, <a href=\"http://cn.engadget.com/category/features/\" rel=\"tag\">独家报道</a></p><div style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"http://cn.engadget.com/2014/01/30/mr-stoneip-lenovo-motorola-insight/\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"http://o.aolcdn.com/hss/storage/adam/85876ca50b9ea4a04be3d903fde60991/1-Lenovo-Buys-Motorola-003-630x354.jpg\" /></a></div>\n<br />\n年三十最大的科技新闻，当然 <a href=\"http://cn.engadget.com/tag/lenovo\">Lenovo</a> 作价 29 亿美元收购曾经红极一时的 <a href=\"http://cn.engadget.com/tag/google\">Google</a> Company - <a href=\"http://cn.engadget.com/tag/motorola\">Motorola</a>。从帐面上来说，Lenovo 收购一家仍在亏损的 Motorola 看似不智，但实际上这却是一宗很有「性价比」的交易。如果你听从一众以为自已系神仙的财经分析师之言，那麽你就错了。<p><br /><p class=\"continueReading\"><a href=\"http://cn.engadget.com/2014/01/30/mr-stoneip-lenovo-motorola-insight/\" rel=\"bookmark\">继续阅读全文 <em>石专栏：Lenovo 收购 Motorola 後，可以预期有什麽改变？</em></a></p><h6 style=\"clear: both; padding: 8px 0 0 0; height: 2px; font-size: 1px; border: 0; margin: 0; padding: 0;\"></h6><a href=\"http://cn.engadget.com/2014/01/30/mr-stoneip-lenovo-motorola-insight/\" rel=\"bookmark\" title=\"Permanent link to this entry\">此文章网址</a>&nbsp;|&nbsp;<a href=\"http://cn.engadget.com/forward/20819223/\" title=\"Send this entry to a friend via email\">转寄此文章</a>&nbsp;|&nbsp;<a href=\"http://cn.engadget.com/2014/01/30/mr-stoneip-lenovo-motorola-insight/#comments\" title=\"View reader comments on this entry\">回应</a><hr size=\"1\" />", 
